    <h1>Restaurant Digital Transformation — CTO Case Study</h1>

    <section class="case-intro">
      <h2>Business context</h2>
      <p>Local restaurant "The Urban Fork" needs a small web solution to: improve customer engagement, manage bookings & simple feedback, and integrate social media to grow presence.</p>

      <div class="restaurant-card">
        <div>
          <h3>The Urban Fork</h3>
          <p>123 Market Lane, Manchester · 0161 555 0123 · open 11:30–22:00</p>
        </div>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a>
